ucci.

00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:12.000
Was it due to the Clinton later to register, you know,

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:14.000
you know, people.

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:24.000
Some peoples that they had names, you know?

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:33.700
And I

00:19:33.700 --> 00:19:37.540
I never got a car all I got it's head up to the letter.

00:19:37.540 --> 00:19:39.380
And was that because of the court?

00:19:39.380 --> 00:19:42.020
Yeah, because the court was all here.

00:19:42.020 --> 00:19:43.020
Okay.

00:19:43.020 --> 00:19:44.740
So your father was one of the people?

00:19:44.740 --> 00:19:51.780
In 64, get my father, my daddy, he was something else in the movie.

00:19:51.780 --> 00:19:52.820
And I'll let him.

00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:55.300
Not to tell me what to do.

00:19:55.300 --> 00:19:56.300
Uh-huh.

00:19:56.300 --> 00:20:02.180
I got registered.

00:20:02.180 --> 00:20:10.780
And I come to that in January, 12 days before Freedom Day.

00:20:10.780 --> 00:20:11.780
Okay.

00:20:11.780 --> 00:20:12.780
So that was in 64?

00:20:12.780 --> 00:20:16.780
Yeah, it was in 64, just guess what?

